{code:xml}
<property name="webwork.multipart.saveDir">/var/opt/confluence/temp</property>
{code}

Using the format above would cause Chart Plugin to fail creating the image containing the chart. The image path url would be: http://home.ibsys.com/download//var/opt/confluence/temp/chartXXXXXpng

