When a user is subscribed to a page that contains a table of contents element {toc}, when he receives notification of edits to that page, the full HTML of that page is included in the e-mail.

All of the links in that e-mail are functional, except for those in the {toc} as they are still in the format of

{code}<a href="#section1">Section 1</a>{code}

